<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Ecobazar</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
    <%- include('../layouts/headerWithoutUser.ejs') %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="bg-green-500 text-white py-20">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Fresh From Farm to Your Table</h1>
            <p class="text-xl opacity-90">Delivering Nature's Best Since 2020</p>
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Story</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Founded in 2020, Ecobazar was born from a simple idea: everyone deserves access to fresh, high-quality produce 
                without leaving their home. What started as a small local delivery service has grown into a comprehensive 
                online marketplace for fresh vegetables, fruits, eggs, meat, and poultry.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Values Grid -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
            <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <div class="text-green-500 text-4xl mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Fresh & Organic</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    We partner with local farmers to bring you the freshest organic produce straight from the farm.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <div class="text-green-500 text-4xl mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-truck"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Fast Delivery</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Same-day delivery ensures your products reach you at their freshest.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <div class="text-green-500 text-4xl mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Quality Guaranteed</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    We stand behind the quality of every product we deliver.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Product Categories -->
        <div class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">What We Offer</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Fresh Vegetables</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Locally sourced, seasonal vegetables delivered fresh daily.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Fresh Fruits</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Sweet and juicy fruits from trusted orchards.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Farm Fresh Eggs</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Free-range eggs from healthy, happy hens.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                    <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Quality Meats</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Premium cuts of meat and fresh poultry products.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sustainability Section -->
        <div class="bg-green-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Commitment to Sustainability</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                    We're committed to sustainable practices throughout our supply chain. From eco-friendly packaging 
                    to supporting local farmers who use sustainable farming methods, we're doing our part to protect 
                    the environment while delivering quality products to your doorstep.
                </p>
                <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-recycle text-green-500 mr-2"></i>
                        <span>Eco-Friendly Packaging</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-seedling text-green-500 mr-2"></i>
                        <span>Sustainable Farming</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart text-green-500 mr-2"></i>
                        <span>Community Support</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../layouts/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html> 